WEBVTT

00:04:54.530 --> 00:05:00.066
Over time, I've come to identify
the optimal conditions

00:05:00.090 --> 00:05:04.328
for these types of creative
and innovative environments

00:05:04.352 --> 00:05:08.356
are clear intent, purpose and passion:

00:05:08.380 --> 00:05:11.614
this is working on something
bigger than ourselves.

00:05:12.730 --> 00:05:14.627
Personal integrity:

00:05:14.651 --> 00:05:17.013
it's doing what we say we're going to do.

00:05:17.037 --> 00:05:20.560
It's being our authentic self
in all interactions.

00:05:20.904 --> 00:05:24.127
Direct communication
and clear expectations,

00:05:24.151 --> 00:05:26.420
even when the subject matter is difficult.

00:05:27.222 --> 00:05:29.167
Grit and perseverance:

00:05:29.191 --> 00:05:32.294
iteration, iteration, iteration.